<taxonomicName authority="Duvivier, 1891" authorityName="Duvivier" authorityYear="1891" class="Insecta" family="Chrysomelidae" genus="Neodera" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Neodera australis" order="Coleoptera" pageId="37" pageNumber="38" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="australis">Neodera australis</taxonomicName>
from specimens from Australia (Queensland); however the generic placement of this species is not correct (C. Reid, 2010, pers. comm.) (Fig. 340).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
